<dd><span class="citation Journal"><a href="/wiki/Benjamin_Whorf" title="Benjamin Whorf" class="mw-redirect"><span class="smallcaps" style="font-variant:small-caps;">Whorf, Benjamin Lee</span></a>; <span class="smallcaps" style="font-variant:small-caps;"><a href="/wiki/Frances_Karttunen" title="Frances Karttunen">Frances Karttunen</a></span> and <span class="smallcaps" style="font-variant:small-caps;"><a href="/wiki/Lyle_Campbell" title="Lyle Campbell">Lyle Campbell</a></span> (1993). "Pitch Tone and the "Saltillo" in Modern and Ancient Nahuatl". <i><a href="/wiki/International_Journal_of_American_Linguistics" title="International Journal of American Linguistics">International Journal of American Linguistics</a></i> (Chicago: <a href="/wiki/University_of_Chicago_Press" title="University of Chicago Press">University of Chicago Press</a>) <b>59</b> (2): 165–223. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1086%2F466194" class="external text" rel="nofollow">10.1086/466194</a>. <a href="/wiki/Online_Computer_Library_Center" title="Online Computer Library Center">OCLC</a>&#160;<a href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/1753556" class="external text" rel="nofollow">1753556</a>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Pitch+Tone+and+the+%22Saltillo%22+in+Modern+and+Ancient+Nahuatl&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BInternational+Journal+of+American+Linguistics%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=%3Cspan+class%3D%22smallcaps%22+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWhorf%2C+Benjamin+Lee%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.au=%3Cspan+class%3D%22smallcaps%22+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWhorf%2C+Benjamin+Lee%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.date=1993&amp;rft.volume=59&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=165%E2%80%93223&amp;rft.place=Chicago&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BUniversity+of+Chicago+Press%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1086%2F466194&amp;rft_id=info:ocl