<dd><span class="citation book"><a href="/wiki/S%C3%B8ren_Wichmann" title="Søren Wichmann"><span class="smallcaps" style="font-variant:small-caps;">Wichmann, Søren</span></a> (1998). "A conservative look at diffusion involving Mixe-Zoquean languages". In Roger Blench and Matthew Spriggs (eds.). <i>Archaeology and Language, vol. II: Correlating archaeological and linguistic hypotheses</i>. One World Archaeology series, <span style="white-space:nowrap;">no. 29</span>. London and New York: <a href="/wiki/Routledge" title="Routledge">Routledge</a>. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-415-11761-5" title="Special:BookSources/0-415-11761-5">0-415-11761-5</a>. <a href="/wiki/Online_Computer_Library_Center" title="Online Computer Library Center">OCLC</a>&#160;<a href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/35673530" class="external text" rel="nofollow">35673530</a>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=A+conservative+look+at+diffusion+involving+Mixe-Zoquean+languages&amp;rft.atitle=Archaeology+and+Language%2C+vol.+II%3A+Correlating+archaeological+and+linguistic+hypotheses&amp;rft.aulast=%3Cspan+class%3D%22smallcaps%22+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWichmann%2C+S%C3%B8ren%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.au=%3Cspan+class%3D%22smallcaps%22+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWichmann%2C+S%C3%B8ren%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.series=One+World+Archaeology+series%2C+%3Cspan+style%3D%22white-space%3Anowrap%3B%22%3Eno.+29%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.place=London+and+New+York&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BRoutledge%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=0-415-11761-5&amp;rft_id=info:oclcnum/35673530&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Nahuatl"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></dd>
<dd><span class="citation web"><span class="smallcaps" style="font-variant:small-caps;">Wimmer, Alexis</span> (2006). <a href="http://sites.estvideo.net/malinal/nahuatl.page.html" class="external text" rel="nofollow">"Dictionnaire de la langue nahuatl classique"</a> (online version, incorporating reproductions from <i>Dictionnaire de la langue nahuatl ou mexicaine</i> [1885], by Rémi Siméon)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://sites.estvideo.net/malinal/nahuatl.page.html" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://sites.estvideo.net/malinal/nahuatl.page.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2008-02-04</span>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Dictionnaire+de+la+langue+nahuatl+classique&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=%3Cspan+class%3D%22smallcaps%22+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWimmer%2C+Alexis%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.au=%3Cspan+class%3D%22smallcaps%22+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWimmer%2C+Alexis%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fsites.estvideo.net%2Fmalinal%2Fnahuatl.page.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Nahuatl"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(French)</span> <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Nahuatl)</span></dd>
